long-description.center: Easy Multicache in North County Dublin
At the given coordinates you will find a couple of signs.
One of these has a series of numbers.
Substitute the letter A for the first number, B for the second, and so on.
The cache location is: N 53째 27.EH(C-B) W 006째 1(D+I).BB(G-H)
